Package: shopr
Title: Gym for Replenishment Decisions of a Shop
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tim", "Radtke", , "tim@timradtke.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Use shopr to simulate sales and inventory of a shop and evaluate
    the forecasts and replenishment decision you make for the shop.
